## Build & Upload
This project is built using PlatformIO + VSCode.

1. Clone the repo
2. Copy `src/config_local.example.hpp` ‚Üí `src/config_local.hpp`
3. Fill Wi-Fi + OpenAI credentials
4. Open with VSCode
5. Click ‚ÄúPlatformIO: Upload‚Äù